<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
    <title>Your Verification Code - Altis Agent CRM</title>
    <style>
        body {
            background-color: #f1f4f9;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            font-family: "Inter", Arial, sans-serif;
            color: #1e293b;
        }

        .wrapper {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 32px 0;
            background-color: #f1f4f9;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 620px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 40px 50px;
            box-shadow: 0 5px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06);
        }

        .logo {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 24px;
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #2563eb;
            letter-spacing: -0.5px;
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 22px;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-bottom: 14px;
            text-align: center;
            color: #0f172a;
        }

        p {
            font-size: 15px;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #475569;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .otp-box {
            display: inline-block;
            margin: 26px auto;
            padding: 16px 24px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            background: #eef2ff;
            color: #1e1b4b;
            font-size: 32px;
            font-weight: 700;
            letter-spacing: 10px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .info {
            font-size: 14px;
            text-align: center;
            color: #64748b;
            margin-top: 12px;
        }

        .footer {
            margin-top: 40px;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #94a3b8;
        }

        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            .container {
                padding: 28px 22px;
            }

            .otp-box {
                font-size: 28px;
                letter-spacing: 8px;
                width: 100%;
            }

            h1 {
                font-size: 20px;
            }

            .logo {
                font-size: 20px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="wrapper">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="logo">Altis Agent CRM</div>

            <h1>Your Verification Code</h1>

            <p>
                Use the OTP below to securely sign in to your CRM account.
                <br />This code is valid for <strong>1 minute</strong>.
            </p>

            <div class="otp-box">{{otp}}</div>

            <p class="info">
                If you did not request this login code, please ignore this message or contact support immediately.
            </p>

            <div class="footer">
                © 2025 Altis Infonet Pvt. Ltd. All rights reserved.<br />
                Secure CRM Platform for Insurance & Financial Agents
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>